label: Gateways and Doorways of Charleston
description: Booklet features "pictures and text arranged in sequence by street on each street, making easy identification of all interesting and historic doorways and gateways."  Also includes map of the Charleston peninsula with points of interest indicated.  Distributed by Legerton & Company, Inc. (Charleston, S.C.).  43 p. : ill., map ; 22 cm.
